Introducing *Pidge Mobile Dashboard*

The Pidge app has always functioned as a powerful, on-the-go extension of
the desktop dashboard.

However, across platforms and conversations, it has often been perceived
simply as =E2=80=9Cthe Pidge app,=E2=80=9D without clearly communicating it=
s true purpose.


To remove ambiguity and reinforce its value, we are formally positioning
the app as the *Pidge Mobile Dashboard*, a companion mobile version of your
desktop operations console.
What This Means For You


Across platforms, documentation, and communication, the app will now be
referred to as *Pidge Mobile Dashboard*.

   -

   Clear understanding that the app is companion to major operational
   aspects of the dashboard
   -

   Seamless continuity between desktop and mobile workflows
   -

   Greater confidence in managing operations directly from your phone



Get the App!
<https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=3Dcom.rindventures.pidgecons=
